snippet.title: Numentale Trailer Q3 2019
snippet.description:
Numentale is a procedurally generated rogue-lite, card-crawling RPG tale with focus on player choice and ensures each adventure is uniquely special. Have a trip through the dark recesses of the dungeon and unlock new content for your next venture to experience your very own Numentale.

Play the game here: https://dragonspark-games.itch.io/numentale
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DragonSparkGame
Discord: http://discord.gg/invite/6aPRxHj
Contact: Dragonsparkgames@gmail.com
